    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may consume a drug or stimulant instead of imbibing an alcoholic drink to gain the drunk status, but you gain the status for double the duration (twice Constitution modifier rounds + 1 per 2 points of base attack bonus). When using hard drinker or any other ability that allows you to rapidly take a drink, you may consume a drug or stimulant instead of a drink (this counts as consuming a stimulant rapidly). You may ignore the negative effects of the drug or addiction so long as you retain the drunk status.</p>\n",
